  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "人気の3DRPGのゲームボーイシリーズ第3作。今回は、より多くの種族、職業、魔法が登場し、通信ケーブルを通じて他のプレイヤーと対戦することも可能です。隠し扉や罠の数々により、難易度はさらに上がりましたが、マニアにはたまらない内容です。マッピング機能のおかげで、携帯デバイスに最適です。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Wizardry Gaiden III: Scripture of the Dark is a Role-Playing game, developed by Sir-Tech Software Inc. and published by ASCII Entertainment, which was released in Japan in 1993.\n\nWhile the first two Gaiden games, Wizardry Gaiden: Suffering of the Queen and Wizardry Gaiden II: Curse of the Ancient Emperor, stuck fairly close to each-other and to Wizardry V: Heart of the Maelstrom, Scripture of the Dark started introducing more radical changes to the formula. This was mostly in the form of incorporating elements of Wizardry VI: Bane of the Cosmic Forge, but retaining the core gameplay derived from Wizardry V.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    }
  ],
